Pierce squash several times with fork or sharp knife. Microwave on HIGH 10 min. or just until softened, turning over after 5 min. Let stand 5 min. Cut squash in half; remove and discard seeds. Use fork to scrape insides of squash to form strands; place in bowl. Add remaining ingredients; toss lightly. Spoon into one of the squash shells; discard remaining squash shell. Microwave on HIGH 2 min. or until heated through.